事为了实现这个简单的东西似乎要重写整个HttpSession类？还有也是因为我们的权限配置是在另一个服务里，所以获取权限的时候要重写UserDetailsService？？不知道是我同事水平不够还是版本太老了，反正看的我是瑟瑟发抖。。。 我就想问一下，有没有必要系统的学习一下这个东西吗？其实我看了半天整个spring security实现的东西似乎和我自己的那种接口思想没什么区别。现在有新项目了，到底要不要系统学习spring security，是我太浅了吗？"},"attached_info":"Cj8IjbPy+NfJ1aF8EAMaCDY0NTY1MjkxIPvKkoUGMAA4swJAC3IJNDYwMjg0ODk0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"61 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f9a7dda1d612568528ed698d674148df_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1713222954.771412","card_id":"Q_339428982","target":{"id":339428982,"title":"考研应该从大三开始就准备吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/339428982","type":"question","created":1565266825,"answer_count":746,"follower_count":3520,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[17566,33814,48430],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IjbPy+NfJ1aF8EAMaCDM3NzA1NTMyIImnsOoFMAA4wBtADHIJMzM5NDI4OTgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-51b312e8edc55b64e880b6f49d564c89_720w.jpg?source=ba7200d9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1713222954.771668","card_id":"Q_644974041","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":644974041,"title":"如果给你一份工作，每看15秒广告就获得1分钱，你会接受吗?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/644974041","type":"question","created":1708357847,"answer_count":92,"follower_count":96,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[937,12585,88888,137155,248